---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { socialLinks } from '../data/social';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Ramy Ghorayeb - Portfolio"
  description="Personal portfolio of Ramy Ghorayeb, Product Manager living between New York & Paris"
>
  <div class="fade-in">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="pt-8 mb-16 max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
        Ramy Ghorayeb
      </h1>

      <!-- Social Links -->
      <div class="flex gap-6 text-sm">
        {socialLinks.map((link) => (
          <a
            href={link.url}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            style="color: var(--color-text);"
          >
            {link.name}
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Me Section -->
    <section class="max-w-2xl mb-24">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <ul class="space-y-6 text-lg" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
            <span><strong>City:</strong> New York & Paris (<a href="https://ramyg.vercel.app/interests/countries" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">list of countries I've been to</a>)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
            <span><strong>Languages:</strong> English, French, Arabic, Spanish</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
            <span><strong>Current Role:</strong> Product Manager - AI/ML & Consumer Products @Uber (<a href="/work" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">more here</a>)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
            <span><strong>Last Education:</strong> Machine Learning & Entrepreneurship @Ecole Polytechnique, France</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Lifestyle:</strong> I Usually Spend Most of My Week Day Evenings and Weekend Days in My Apartment Learning or Building Stuff, Then Go on Weekend Nights bc I've Spent Too Much Time Alone
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Topics I Love:</strong> Geopolitics, French Politics, Middle Eastern History, Economy, Startups, AI, Longevity & Biohacking (<a href="/interests/longevity" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">find my protocol here</a>), Personal Finance, Productivity, Relationships, Sci-fi, Postmodern Literature, Mangas, Glitch Art, French Real Estate, Survivalism, Antiquity and Renaissance Sculptures, Music (Guitar, Piano, Oud, Ableton, DJ), Video (Editing, Motion Design, 2D/Pseudo-3D VFX)
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Things I Am Discovering:</strong> Religious Archeology, Theology, Chess, Jungian Psychology, Camusian Philosophy, Yu-gi-oh Cards Strategy, Pokemon Strategy, Game Design
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Things I Value:</strong> Loyalty, Transparency, Taste, Opinions, Freedom of Thought, Strong Ego but Well Placed
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Random Things I Can Recommend</strong> (<a href="https://ramyg.vercel.app/interests/recommendations" class="hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-link);">more here</a>):
              <ul class="ml-6 mt-2 space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span><strong>Food:</strong> Taouk + Hummus + Fattoush</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span><strong>Fiction:</strong> Liu Cixin - The Immortal Death</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span><strong>Non-Fiction:</strong> Chuck Palahniuk - Stranger Than Fiction: True Stories</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span><strong>Self Development:</strong> R. Moore & D. Gillette - King, Warrior, Magician, Lover</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span><strong>Biography:</strong> Cizia Zyke - Oro</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span><strong>Manga:</strong> Jiro Taniguchi - The Summit of the Gods</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span><strong>Music Album:</strong> Steven Wilson - Insurgentes</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span><strong>Movie:</strong> Mr Fantastic (Not a Superhero Movie)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="mr-2">•</span>
                  <span><strong>TV Show:</strong> The Leftovers</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Random Fun Stuff I've Done:</strong> Built YouTube Channels, with One of Them Growing Up to 180k+ Subscribers, Lived in a Boxing Camp in Thailand, Ran a Life Coaching Business, Worked at a Music Label in France
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Games I Will Crush You At:</strong> Super Smash Bros Melee, Mario Kart DS
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="mr-3" style="color: var(--color-warm-accent);">•</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Things I Want to Do:</strong> Build a Classical Stone Sculpture, Climb Up the Mont Blanc, Perform a Planche, Learn Poker, Get My Skydiving License, Release a Compilation Album of Dictators Propaganda Music (Yes), Complete My Self Constitution
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</PageLayout>
